;\n  }\n\n  .technical-fabrics-page .faq-item {\n    background-color: white;\n    margin-bottom: 15px;\n    border-radius: 10px;\n    overflow: hidden;\n    box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);\n  }\n\n  .technical-fabrics-page .faq-question {\n    padding: 20px;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    cursor: pointer;\n    display: flex;\n    justify-content: space-between;\n    align-items: center;\n    color: #000000;\n  }\n\n  .technical-fabrics-page .faq-question i {\n    transition: transform 0.3s;\n  }\n\n  .technical-fabrics-page .faq-item.active .faq-question i {\n    transform: rotate(180deg);\n  }\n\n  .technical-fabrics-page .faq-answer {\n    padding: 0 20px;\n    max-height: 0;\n    overflow: hidden;\n    transition: max-height 0.3s, padding 0.3s;\n  }\n\n  .technical-fabrics-page .faq-item.active .faq-answer {\n    padding: 0 20px 20px;\n    max-height: 500px;\n  }\n\n  /* CTA Section */\n  .technical-fabrics-page .cta {\n    background: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7)), url('https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0857/0902/9660/files/tech_fabric1.png?v=1759226239');\n    background-size: cover;\n    background-position: center;\n    color: white;\n    text-align: center;\n    padding: 100px 0;\n    margin-top: 60px;\n  }\n\n  .technical-fabrics-page .cta h2 {\n    font-size: 2.5rem;\n    margin-bottom: 20px;\ncolor: #ffffff\n  }\n\n  .technical-fabrics-page .cta p {\n    font-size: 1.2rem;\n    max-width: 700px;\n    margin: 0 auto 30px;\n  }\n\n  /* Responsive Styles */\n  @media (max-width: 768px) {\n    .technical-fabrics-page .hero h1 {\n      font-size: 2rem;\n    }\n\n    .technical-fabrics-page .hero p {\n      font-size: 1rem;\n    }\n\n    .technical-fabrics-page .section-title {\n      font-size: 2rem;\n    }\n\n    .technical-fabrics-page .fabric-tabs {\n      overflow-x: auto;\n      -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;\n    }\n\n    .technical-fabrics-page .care-steps {\n      grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n    }\n\n    .technical-fabrics-page .usage-frequency {\n      grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n    }\n\n    .technical-fabrics-page .btn {\n      margin-right: 0;\n      margin-bottom: 10px;\n    }\n  }\n\n  @media (max-width: 992px) {\n    .technical-fabrics-page .care-steps {\n      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);\n    }\n  }\n</style>\n\n<div class=\"technical-fabrics-page\">\n  <!-- Hero Section -->\n  <div class=\"hero\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n      <h1>Technical Fabrics in Men's Clothing</h1>\n      <p>Key Types, Their Benefits & How to Choose</p>\n      <p>When it comes to choosing the right clothing, the fabric matters more than you might think. Whether you're gearing up for a busy day in the city or braving the elements outdoors, the right fabric can make all the difference in comfort, performance, and durability.</p>\n      <a href=\"#fabrics\" class=\"btn\">Explore Fabric Types</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"container\">\n    <!-- About Technical Fabric Section -->\n    <section id=\"about\">\n      <h2 class=\"section-title\">What is Technical Fabric?</h2>\n      <p class=\"section-subtitle\">Technical fabric is a type of material specifically engineered to serve a functional purpose beyond regular fabric.</p>\n      <div class=\"about-content\">\n        <div class=\"about-text\">\n          <p>Technical fabric is a type of material specifically engineered to serve a functional purpose beyond regular fabric. Unlike traditional fabrics, technical fabrics are designed to provide enhanced performance, such as water resistance, breathability, durability, or thermal regulation. These fabrics are typically used in clothing and gear that require specialized features for outdoor activities, sports, or other high-performance environments.</p>\n          <p>At Alpargali, we've taken a step beyond traditional fabrics, using advanced technical materials designed to support your lifestyle. In this guide, we'll break down what makes technical fabrics so special, how they outperform regular cloth, and why they're the smart choice for your wardrobe.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"about-image\">\n          <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0857/0902/9660/files/tech_fabric2.png?v=1759226239\" alt=\"Technical Fabric\">\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <!-- Fabric Uses Section -->\n    <section>\n      <h2 class=\"section-title\">What is Tech Cloth Used For?</h2>\n      <p class=\"section-subtitle\">Tech fabrics are all about making your life easier—whether it's keeping you comfortable, protected, or looking fresh.</p>\n      <div class=\"features-grid\">\n        <div class=\"feature-card\">\n          <div class=\"feature-icon\">\n            <i class=\"fas fa-running\"></i>\n          </div>\n          <h3>Sportswear</h3>\n          <p>Clothes that need to stretch, breathe, and wick away moisture—perfect for running, gym workouts, or any active pursuit.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"feature-card\">\n          <div class=\"feature-icon\">\n            <i class=\"fas fa-mountain\"></i>\n          </div>\n          <h3>Outdoor Gear</h3>\n          <p>Jackets, pants, and other gear for things like hiking or skiing where you need both weather protection and breathability.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"feature-card\">\n          <div class=\"feature-icon\">\n            <i class=\"fas fa-hard-hat\"></i>\n          </div>\n          <h3>Workwear</h3>\n          <p>Tough, durable fabrics that can handle hard work while keeping you comfortable—whether it's for labor-intensive jobs or outdoor work.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"feature-card\">\n          <div class=\"feature-icon\">\n            <i class=\"fas fa-suitcase\"></i>\n          </div>\n          <h3>Travel Clothing</h3>\n          <p>Fabrics that resist wrinkles, stains, and odors, making them perfect for trips when you need your clothes to look fresh even after a long day.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <!-- Fabric Types Section -->\n    <section id=\"fabrics\">\n      <h2 class=\"section-title\">Our Technical Fabric List</h2>\n      <p class=\"section-subtitle\">Explore our selection of high-performance fabrics, each designed for specific needs.</p>\n      \n      <div class=\"fabric-tabs\">\n        <div class=\"fabric-tab active\" data-tab=\"sorona\">Sorona Fabric</div>\n        <div class=\"fabric-tab\" data-tab=\"aerogel\">Aerogel Insulation</div>\n        <div class=\"fabric-tab\" data-tab=\"graphene\">Graphene Fabric</div>\n        <div class=\"fabric-tab\" data-tab=\"teflon\">Teflon-Coated Fabric</div>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"fabric-content active\" id=\"sorona\">\n        <div class=\"fabric-details\">\n          <div class=\"fabric-info\">\n            <h3>Sorona Fabric: Eco-Friendliness Meets Comfort</h3>\n            <p>At Alpargali, we prioritize sustainability without sacrificing performance. Sorona fabric, made from a mix of plant-based and petroleum-based fibers, combines eco-friendly properties with comfort. Soft, breathable, and with just the right amount of stretch, it's ideal for both active wear and everyday use.</p>\n            <p>We use Sorona in key pieces like the Alpargali Aerogel Graphene Puffer Jacket and Graphene Vest, providing you with flexibility and comfort whether you're layering up or on the move.</p>\n            <div class=\"fabric-properties\">\n              <span class=\"property-tag\">Eco-friendly</span>\n              <span class=\"property-tag\">Soft</span>\n              <span class=\"property-tag\">Lightweight</span>\n              <span class=\"property-tag\">Stretchy</span>\n              <span class=\"property-tag\">Recyclable</span>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"btn-group\">\n              <a href=\"https://www.alpargali.com/blogs/tech-fabric/sorona\" class=\"btn\">Learn More</a>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"fabric-image\">\n            <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0857/0902/9660/files/tech_fabric3.png?v=1759226239\" alt=\"Sorona Fabric\">\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"fabric-content\" id=\"aerogel\">\n        <div class=\"fabric-details\">\n          <div class=\"fabric-info\">\n            <h3>Aerogel Insulation: Lightweight Warmth for Every Season</h3>\n            <p>Aerogel insulation is known for being one of the lightest yet most efficient materials for warmth. It keeps you warm without adding bulk, making it perfect for cold weather without feeling heavy. We use Aerogel in the Alpargali Aerogel Graphene Puffer Jacket, giving you the ideal combination of warmth and lightweight comfort. It's breathable, too, making it suitable for varying weather conditions.</p>\n            <div class=\"fabric-properties\">\n              <span class=\"property-tag\">Ultra-light</span>\n              <span class=\"property-tag\">Superior warmth</span>\n              <span class=\"property-tag\">Thin</span>\n              <span class=\"property-tag\">Breathable</span>\n              <span class=\"property-tag\">Suitable for various weather</span>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"btn-group\">\n              <a href=\"https://www.alpargali.com/blogs/tech-fabric/aerogel\" class=\"btn\">Learn More</a>\n              <a href=\"https://www.alpargali.com/blogs/tech-fabric/aerogel-vs-down\" class=\"btn\">About Aerogel vs Down</a>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"fabric-image\">\n            <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0857/0902/9660/files/tech_fabric4.png?v=1759226239\" alt=\"Aerogel Insulation\">\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"fabric-content\" id=\"graphene\">\n        <div class=\"fabric-details\">\n          <div class=\"fabric-info\">\n            <h3>Graphene Fabric: A Future-Ready Material</h3>\n            <p>Graphene fabric is the future of high-performance textiles. Known for its strength and temperature-regulating properties, graphene adapts to your body's needs, offering comfort in both hot and cold conditions. It's also antimicrobial and UV-resistant, making it durable and fresh. We incorporate Graphene in several of our designs, including the Aerogel Graphene Puffer Jacket and Graphene Vest, combining technology with practicality.</p>\n            <div class=\"fabric-properties\">\n              <span class=\"property-tag\">Strong</span>\n              <span class=\"property-tag\">Lightweight</span>\n              <span class=\"property-tag\">Temperature-regulating</span>\n              <span class=\"property-tag\">Antimicrobial</span>\n              <span class=\"property-tag\">UV-resistant</span>\n              <span class=\"property-tag\">Durable</span>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"btn-group\">\n              <a href=\"https://www.alpargali.com/blogs/tech-fabric/graphene\" class=\"btn\">Learn More</a>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"fabric-image\">\n            <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0857/0902/9660/files/tech_fabric5.png?v=1759226239\" alt=\"Graphene Fabric\">\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"fabric-content\" id=\"teflon\">\n        <div class=\"fabric-details\">\n          <div class=\"fabric-info\">\n            <h3>Teflon-Coated Fabric: Protection and Durability Combined</h3>\n            <p>Teflon-coated fabric provides waterproofing, stain resistance, and durability. The coating acts as a shield, making it perfect for outerwear and activewear that need to withstand the elements. We use this fabric in the Aerogel Graphene Puffer Jacket and Graphene Vest, ensuring protection from weather and stains while keeping your gear looking great with minimal care.</p>\n            <div class=\"fabric-properties\">\n              <span class=\"property-tag\">Waterproof</span>\n              <span class=\"property-tag\">Stain-resistant</span>\n              <span class=\"property-tag\">Durable</span>\n              <span class=\"property-tag\">Easy to clean</span>\n              <span class=\"property-tag\">Breathable</span>\n              <span class=\"property-tag\">High-level protection</span>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"btn-group\">\n              <a href=\"https://www.alpargali.com/blogs/tech-fabric/teflon-coated\" class=\"btn\">Learn More</a>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"fabric-image\">\n            <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0857/0902/9660/files/tech_fabric6.png?v=1759226239\" alt=\"Teflon-Coated Fabric\">\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <!-- How to Choose Section -->\n    <section>\n      <h2 class=\"section-title\">How to Choose the Right Technical Fabric for You</h2>\n      <p class=\"section-subtitle\">At Alpargali, we understand that choosing the right product is about finding the perfect balance between performance, comfort, and style.</p>\n      \n      <div class=\"features-grid\">\n        <div class=\"feature-card\">\n          <div class=\"feature-icon\">\n            <i class=\"fas fa-fire\"></i>\n          </div>\n          <h3>Looking for Warmth Without the Bulk?</h3>\n          <p>If you want something that will keep you warm in cold weather but still feel lightweight and comfortable, the Alpargali Aerogel Graphene Puffer Jacket is the one for you. With Aerogel insulation, this jacket offers excellent warmth without the heavy feel.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"feature-card\">\n          <div class=\"feature-icon\">\n            <i class=\"fas fa-running\"></i>\n          </div>\n          <h3>Need Active Comfort for Workouts or Outdoor Activities?</h3>\n          <p>If you're after something that moves with you, provides stretch, and feels comfortable for a variety of activities, the Graphene Lightweight Jacket or Graphene Vest are great choices. Both are made with Sorona fabric, which is breathable, antimicrobial, and soft.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"feature-card\">\n          <div class=\"feature-icon\">\n            <i class=\"fas fa-tint-slash\"></i>\n          </div>\n          <h3>Want to Stay Dry in Wet Conditions?</h3>\n          <p>If you need protection from the rain or want something that's low-maintenance and easy to clean, the Alpargali Aerogel Graphene Puffer Jacket with Teflon-coated fabric is a solid option. The Teflon coating makes it resistant to water, stains, and dirt.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"feature-card\">\n          <div class=\"feature-icon\">\n            <i class=\"fas fa-leaf\"></i>\n          </div>\n          <h3>Caring About Sustainability?</h3>\n          <p>If you're looking for something more sustainable without sacrificing performance, Sorona fabric is an excellent choice. Used in the Graphene Vest and Graphene Lightweight Jacket, Sorona offers eco-friendly properties while maintaining a high level of comfort, breathability, and stretch.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <!-- Comparison Section -->\n    <section style=\"background-color: #f8f8f8; padding: 60px 0;\">\n      <h2 class=\"section-title\">What is the Difference Between Technical Cloth and Regular Cloth?</h2>\n      <p class=\"section-subtitle\">At Alpargali, we believe in performance over basics. Here's why our technical fabric menswear is a better choice than regular cloth:</p>\n      \n      <table class=\"comparison-table\">\n        <thead>\n          <tr>\n            <th>Feature</th>\n            <th>Technical Fabric</th>\n            <th>Regular Cloth</th>\n          </tr>\n        </thead>\n        <tbody>\n          <tr>\n            <td>Performance</td>\n            <td><i class=\"fas fa-check check-icon\"></i> Designed for functionality—waterproofing, breathability, or temperature regulation</td>\n            <td><i class=\"fas fa-times times-icon\"></i> More about comfort and style, lacks specialized features</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <td>Durability</td>\n            <td><i class=\"fas fa-check check-icon\"></i> Graphene and Teflon-coated fabrics are built to last, resist wear, stains, and weather</td>\n            <td><i class=\"fas fa-times times-icon\"></i> Don't hold up as well over time, can lose shape or performance quickly</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <td>Comfort and Flexibility</td>\n            <td><i class=\"fas fa-check check-icon\"></i> Stretchy, breathable, and moisture-wicking—perfect for active lifestyles</td>\n            <td><i class=\"fas fa-times times-icon\"></i> Doesn't provide the same comfort or adaptability during physical activity</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <td>Protection from the Elements</td>\n            <td><i class=\"fas fa-check check-icon\"></i> Use fabrics like Gore-Tex to keep you dry and comfortable in rain or wind</td>\n            <td><i class=\"fas fa-times times-icon\"></i> Offers little protection in these conditions</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <td>Sustainability</td>\n            <td><i class=\"fas fa-check check-icon\"></i> Sorona fabric, made with plant-based fibers, gives you performance with an eco-friendly focus</td>\n            <td><i class=\"fas fa-times times-icon\"></i> Regular cloth often lacks this eco-friendly aspect</td>\n          </tr>\n        </tbody>\n      </table>\n    </section>\n\n    <!-- Care Section -->\n    <section>\n      <h2 class=\"section-title\">How to Wash and Care for Technical Fabrics</h2>\n      <p class=\"section-subtitle\">To keep your Alpargali garments in top condition, follow these simple care guidelines:</p>\n      \n      <div class=\"care-steps\">\n        <div class=\"care-step\">\n          <h3><i class=\"fas fa-soap\"></i> Use a Mild Detergent</h3>\n          <p>Always use a mild, neutral detergent that does not contain fabric softeners. Fabric softeners can damage the performance of technical fabrics by coating the fibers and reducing their breathability and water resistance.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"care-step\">\n          <h3><i class=\"fas fa-ban\"></i> No Bleaching</h3>\n          <p>Avoid bleach or any harsh chemicals, as they can break down the fibers and affect the fabric's performance.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"care-step\">\n          <h3><i class=\"fas fa-hand-sparkles\"></i> Gentle Wash</h3>\n          <p>Use a gentle wash cycle with cold or lukewarm water to prevent any damage to the fabric or its treatments. Technical fabrics need gentle care to maintain their effectiveness.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"care-step\">\n          <h3><i class=\"fas fa-iron\"></i> Iron Carefully</h3>\n          <p>Avoid direct contact between the iron soleplate and the fabric. If ironing is needed, use a low temperature and iron the garment inside out to protect the fabric's surface.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"care-step\">\n          <h3><i class=\"fas fa-temperature-low\"></i> Low-Temperature Tumble Dry</h3>\n          <p>If you use a dryer, make sure it's on a low-temperature setting. High heat can damage the technical coatings and reduce the fabric's performance.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"care-step\">\n          <h3><i class=\"fas fa-tshirt\"></i> Dry Clean</h3>\n          <p>Dry cleaning is an option for certain garments, especially those with delicate treatments or finishes. Always check the care label for specific instructions.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      \n      <h3 style=\"margin-top: 40px; text-align: center;\">Usage and Cleaning Frequency</h3>\n      <div class=\"usage-frequency\">\n        <div class=\"care-step\">\n          <h3><i class=\"fas fa-running\"></i> Intensive Use</h3>\n          <p>If your garment is used frequently for high-intensity activities, deep clean it after approximately 10 uses to maintain its performance.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"care-step\">\n          <h3><i class=\"fas fa-walking\"></i> Low-Intensity Use</h3>\n          <p>For less frequent use, deep clean your garment every 1-2 months to keep it in optimal condition.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <!-- Products Section -->\n    <section id=\"products\">\n      <h2 class=\"section-title\">Explore Our Products</h2>\n      <p class=\"section-subtitle\">Discover the perfect piece that combines innovation, comfort, and style.</p>\n      \n      <div class=\"products-grid\">\n        <div class=\"product-card\">\n          <div class=\"product-image\">\n            <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0857/0902/9660/files/tech_fabric7.png?v=1759226239\" alt=\"Aerogel Graphene Puffer Jacket\">\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"product-info\">\n            <h3>Alpargali Aerogel Graphene Puffer Jacket</h3>\n            <p>Featuring Aerogel insulation and Graphene fabric for unparalleled warmth and lightweight comfort. Teflon coating ensures water and stain resistance.</p>\n            <a href=\"https://www.alpargali.com/products/alpargali-aerogel-graphene-puffer-jacket\" class=\"btn\">View Details</a>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"product-card\">\n          <div class=\"product-image\">\n            <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0857/0902/9660/files/tech_fabric8.png?v=1759226239\" alt=\"Graphene Lightweight Jacket\">\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"product-info\">\n            <h3>Graphene Lightweight Jacket</h3>\n            <p>Made with Sorona fabric and Graphene technology for exceptional breathability, antimicrobial properties, and temperature regulation. Perfect for various activities.</p>\n            <a href=\"https://www.alpargali.com/products/graphene-lightweight-jacket\" class=\"btn\">View Details</a>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"product-card\">\n          <div class=\"product-image\">\n            <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0857/0902/9660/files/tech_fabric9.png?v=1759226239\" alt=\"Graphene Vest\">\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"product-info\">\n            <h3>Graphene Vest</h3>\n            <p>Combining Sorona and Graphene fabrics for lightweight warmth and flexibility. Perfect mid-layer for various weather conditions.</p>\n            <a href=\"https://www.alpargali.com/products/graphene-vest\" class=\"btn\">View Details</a>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <!-- FAQ Section -->\n    <section id=\"faq\">\n      <h2 class=\"section-title\">FAQs about Technical Fabric</h2>\n      <p class=\"section-subtitle\">Find answers to your questions about technical fabrics.</p>\n      \n      <div class=\"faq-container\">\n        <div class=\"faq-item\">\n          <div class=\"faq-question\">\n            Is technical fabric stretchy?\n            <i class=\"fas fa-chevron-down\"></i>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n            <p>Yes, many technical fabrics, like Sorona and Graphene, offer excellent stretchability for comfort and flexibility, especially in activewear and performance garments.</p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"faq-item\">\n          <div class=\"faq-question\">\n            Is technical fabric warm?\n            <i class=\"fas fa-chevron-down\"></i>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n            <p>Some technical fabrics, like Aerogel insulation, are specifically designed to provide warmth without the bulk, making them perfect for cold weather. Other fabrics, like Graphene, help regulate temperature, keeping you comfortable in various conditions.</p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"faq-item\">\n          <div class=\"faq-question\">\n            Is technical fabric waterproof?\n            <i class=\"fas fa-chevron-down\"></i>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n            <p>Some technical fabrics, such as Gore-Tex and Teflon-coated fabrics, are designed to be water-resistant or waterproof. These fabrics help protect you from the elements, keeping you dry in rainy or wet conditions.</p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"faq-item\">\n          <div class=\"faq-question\">\n            What fabric is 100% waterproof?\n            <i class=\"fas fa-chevron-down\"></i>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n            <p>There are no fabrics that are entirely waterproof without treatment. However, Gore-Tex and Teflon-coated fabrics are highly waterproof, offering excellent protection against water and rain.</p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"faq-item\">\n          <div class=\"faq-question\">\n            Which fabric is best for heavy winter?\n            <i class=\"fas fa-chevron-down\"></i>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n            <p>For heavy winter, Aerogel insulation is ideal due to its lightweight warmth. It traps heat efficiently without adding bulk, making it perfect for cold, winter conditions.</p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"faq-item\">\n          <div class=\"faq-question\">\n            What is so special about tech fleece?\n            <i class=\"fas fa-chevron-down\"></i>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n            <p>Tech fleece is designed for warmth without weight. It's typically made from materials like Polartec and is soft, insulating, and breathable, making it perfect for layering or active use in colder weather.</p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"faq-item\">\n          <div class=\"faq-question\">\n            What is the unhealthiest fabric to wear?\n            <i class=\"fas fa-chevron-down\"></i>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n            <p>Fabrics with high amounts of synthetic chemicals or non-breathable materials, such as some cheap polyester blends, can trap sweat and bacteria, potentially causing skin irritation. Always opt for breathable, natural, or high-tech fabrics like Sorona and Graphene for better skin comfort and health.</p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- CTA Section -->\n  <div class=\"cta\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n      <h2>Ready to experience the difference for yourself?</h2>\n      <p>Explore our collection and find the perfect piece that combines innovation, comfort, and style. Your next adventure starts here.</p>\n      <a href=\"#products\" class=\"btn\">Explore Now</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<script>\n  // Fabric Tabs Functionality\n  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {\n    const tabs = document.querySelectorAll('.technical-fabrics-page .fabric-tab');\n    const contents = document.querySelectorAll('.technical-fabrics-page .fabric-content');\n    \n    tabs.forEach(tab => {\n      tab.addEventListener('click', () => {\n        const tabId = tab.getAttribute('data-tab');\n        \n        // Remove active class from all tabs and contents\n        tabs.forEach(t => t.classList.remove('active'));\n        contents.forEach(c => c.classList.remove('active'));\n        \n        // Add active class to clicked tab and corresponding content\n        tab.classList.add('active');\n        document.getElementById(tabId).classList.add('active');\n      });\n    });\n    \n    // FAQ Accordion\n    const faqItems = document.querySelectorAll('.technical-fabrics-page .faq-item');\n    \n    faqItems.forEach(item => {\n      const question = item.querySelector('.faq-question');\n      \n      question.addEventListener('click', () => {\n        // Toggle active class on clicked item\n     